name: The BEST CREW EVER? WestJet Encore Dash 8-400 Montreal to Toronto
description:
In February, I flew with WestJet Encore between Montreal and Toronto on their Bombardier Q400/De Havilland Canada Dash 8-400.

I booked this trip as part of flying on the first revenue flight of WestJet’s Dreamliner in February, from Toronto to Calgary, so I decided to make a side trip to Montreal beforehand.

See what I thought of WestJet Encore in this trip report!

Shoutout to Will for laughing at my pain https://www.instagram.com/willrdaviation
